  "title": "Injectable",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/di/injectable.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L68-L69\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/7.0.0/packages/core/src/di/injectable.ts#L68-L69\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/Injectable\", \"name\": \"Injectable\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n  </div>\n  \n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"injectable\">Injectable<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Injectable#injectable\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label decorator\">decorator</label>\n    \n    \n    \n  </header>\n  \n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p>A marker metadata that marks a class as available to <code><a href=\"api/core/Injector\" class=\"code-anchor\">Injector</a></code> for creation.</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/core/Injectable#description\">See more...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  \n  \n  \n\n\n<section class=\"decorator-overview\">\n  \n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table option-overview\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr><th>Option</th><th>Description</th></tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"option\">\n      <td>\n        <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/Injectable#providedIn\">\n          <code>providedIn</code>\n        </a>\n      </td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n\n  \n  \n  \n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Injectable#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p>For more details, see the <a href=\"guide/dependency-injection\">\"Dependency Injection Guide\"</a>.</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n<section class=\"decorator-options\">\n  <h2 id=\"options\">Options<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Injectable#options\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n  <a id=\"providedIn\"></a>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width option-table\">\n    <thead><tr><th>\n      <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n        <h3 id=\"providedin\">providedIn<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Injectable#providedin\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n        <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/di/injectable.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L60-L59\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/7.0.0/packages/core/src/di/injectable.ts#L60-L59\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n      </div>\n    </th></tr></thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n          <a href=\"api/core/Injectable#providedIn\" class=\"code-anchor\">providedIn</a>: <a href=\"api/core/Type\" class=\"code-anchor\">Type</a>&#x3C;any> | 'root' | null\n          </code-example>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n  \n</section>\n\n  \n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">Usage notes<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Injectable#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <h3 id=\"example\">Example<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Injectable#example\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<code-example path=\"core/di/ts/metadata_spec.ts\" region=\"Injectable\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Injectable\" class=\"code-anchor\">Injectable</a>()\nclass UsefulService {\n}\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Injectable\" class=\"code-anchor\">Injectable</a>()\nclass NeedsService {\n  constructor(public service: UsefulService) {}\n}\n\nconst injector = ReflectiveInjector.resolveAndCreate([NeedsService, UsefulService]);\nexpect(injector.get(NeedsService).service instanceof UsefulService).toBe(true);\n\n</code-example>\n<p><code><a href=\"api/core/Injector\" class=\"code-anchor\">Injector</a></code> will throw an error when trying to instantiate a class that\ndoes not have <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Injectable\" class=\"code-anchor\">Injectable</a></code> marker, as shown in the example below.</p>\n<code-example path=\"core/di/ts/metadata_spec.ts\" region=\"InjectableThrows\">\nclass UsefulService {}\n\nclass NeedsService {\n  constructor(public service: UsefulService) {}\n}\n\nexpect(() => ReflectiveInjector.resolveAndCreate([NeedsService, UsefulService])).toThrow();\n\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common/NgComponentOutlet\n - api/core\n - api/core/ConstructorSansProvider\n - api/core/Inject\n - api/core/InjectableProvider\n - api/core/InjectionToken\n - api/core/Optional\n - api/core/ReflectiveInjector\n - api/core/Self\n - api/core/SkipSelf\n - api/core/TypeProvider\n - api/core/defineInjectable\n - api/http/Request\n - api/http/testing/MockBackend\n - api/router/CanActivate\n - api/router/CanActivateChild\n - api/router/CanDeactivate\n - api/router/CanLoad\n - api/router/Resolve\n - api/upgrade/UpgradeAdapter\n - api/upgrade/static/downgradeInjectable\n - guide/aot-compiler\n - guide/architecture-services\n - guide/cheatsheet\n - guide/component-interaction\n - guide/dependency-injection\n - guide/dependency-injection-in-action\n - guide/dependency-injection-providers\n - guide/dynamic-form\n - guide/elements\n - guide/form-validation\n - guide/glossary\n - guide/hierarchical-dependency-injection\n - guide/http\n - guide/ngmodule-faq\n - guide/providers\n - guide/router\n - guide/service-worker-communications\n - guide/singleton-services\n - guide/styleguide\n - guide/testing\n - guide/upgrade\n - tutorial/toh-pt4\n - tutorial/toh-pt5\n - tutorial/toh-pt6\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/Injectable#description\n - api/core/Injectable#example\n - api/core/Injectable#injectable\n - api/core/Injectable#options\n - api/core/Injectable#providedIn\n - api/core/Injectable#providedin\n - api/core/Injectable#usage-notes\n - api/core/Injector\n - api/core/Type\n - guide/dependency-injection\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/di/injectable.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L60-L59\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/di/injectable.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L68-L69